children.subject: Sorry for the late response! The best time to apply is any time from now till the end of October, although the sooner the better. We're planning on releasing our beta product late August and would love to have for some more people to be part of that.
HI! When is the best time to apply? I still need to get my resume checked.

history.content:
Hi everyone!

The startup I'm interning at for the summer is looking to hire software engineers for their team. I'm helping them look for both a backend developer and a fullstack developer to start around Fall or afterwards.

A bit about the company: 21 Labs, Inc. is developing an automatic mobile application tester to optimise the QA process. We're based in Campbell, CA (near San Jose) and are about to go into beta with our product, so you will be building a lot in the main application.

Please refer to the job descriptions below if you're interested! If you have any specific questions or are interested, please email royihaddad@gmail.com and attach your resume as well. Thank you!
